{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b9aac9be-a49b-4b96-b828-6c4245942c8f","content":"`.testsettings` files are **not supported in MSTest v3** — you need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your `.testsettings` configures and how each maps:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` (30s) | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>` |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>` |\n| Code Coverage data collector | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n\nLet me create the replacement `.runsettings` and update your project:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01CVj2devXU9Zgcm4t2gbU4w","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01WaK6g7skYoV9Ro2Mx5D2XQ","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-5c50ad4ccb4b4463b3c1dd036b4f8416/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>false</DeploymentEnabled>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.dll\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-5c50ad4ccb4b4463b3c1dd036b4f8416/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01VFMRViw4BrJXKEgbpq1kWi","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-5c50ad4ccb4b4463b3c1dd036b4f8416/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.8.0\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>","new_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\local.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.8.0\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-5c50ad4ccb4b4463b3c1dd036b4f8416/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"3b001d62-e86d-45a0-9042-a490bea28fad","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Assembly resolution / test deployment config\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The configuration needs to be migrated to a `.runsettings` file and/or MSTest v3 attributes/properties.\n\nLet me explain the migration:\n\n1. **Test timeout** → Use `[Timeout]` attribute on test methods, or set a default timeout in `.runsettings` via `<MSTest><TestTimeout>`.\n\n\n2. **Code coverage data collector** → Configure in `.runsettings` under `<DataCollectionRunSettings>`.\n3. **Assembly resolution / deployment** → MSTest v3 handles deployment differently; the `useLoadContext` setting maps to `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>` in `.runsettings`.\n\nI need to create a `.runsettings` file that replaces the `.testsettings` configuration.","outputTokens":1021,"requestId":"240A:341029:46451A:4B0451:6A031072"},"id":"62b037b4-3aa6-4d07-9b01-b2223bb7d8e7","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:35:28.881Z","parentId":"aa5173cb-1fc3-4f0c-8940-429fc6f5f2c9"}
